            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> pepper strips</strong>,<strong> red onion wedges </strong>and<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until softened and beginning to colour – these are your <strong>roasted vegetables</strong></p>",
