            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 15 min or until the orzo is tender with a slight bite</p><p>Tip: Stir the orzo occasionally to prevent it from sticking!</p>",
      "order": 5,
