    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo is cooked, add the <strong>roasted vegetables </strong>to the pan with the <strong>red wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basil </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>roasted red pepper orzo</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if your orzo is looking a little dry!</p>",
