    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted red pepper orzo</strong> in bowls</p><p>Crumble the <strong>goats' cheese </strong>all over the top</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved basil leaves </strong>and<strong> </strong>a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong>, then season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
